title: McCallie Music Video Creating Waves Before Baylor Rivalry Game
text: Updated: 3:24 pm Chattanooga (WDEF) - What's the best high school rivalry in the Tennessee Valley?Some students are making their case for the annual Baylor/McCallie grudge match with a new music video.A Spirit Week project at McCallie led to a re-written version of Jay-Z's "Run This Town."They recruited a recent alumnus for lyrics and the sound recording and got some help from a GPS junior.The video is now getting national play online for the best spirit video of the year, including BleacherReport.com, FanBuzz.com, Nextimpulsesports.comTake a look.
